2164.subject: ENSTU
2164.descrlong:
Assists students enrolled in a group capstone project course in preparing their final written report, poster, and/or oral presentation for their senior capstone process.  Students will also complete their ENSTU e-portfolio.   Students must co-enroll in ENSTU 471 or another approved capstone projects course.

[Prereq: (ENSTU 300 or BIO 300 or ENVS 300 or MSCI 300) and (Coreq: ENSTU 471)]
